Trainers, this legendary week of Raid Battles is heating up! Heading into the weekend, #TeamRayquaza leads by a margin of 52% vs. 48%. Can #TeamKyogre & #TeamGroudon make a comeback?

Remember Trainers, if Rayquaza is defeated more than Kyogre and Groudon combined by 3/5, Pokémon that prefer windy weather will be more likely to hatch from Eggs starting 3/5. If not, Pokémon that prefer sunny or rainy weather will be more likely to hatch.
Did you know? Rayquaza is said to have lived for hundreds of millions of years. The Sky High Pokémon is also the first Legendary Dragon-type Pokémon available in Pokémon GO! #TeamRayquaza

Aggron can learn Charged Attacks of different types—Rock-type Stone Edge, Electric-type Thunder, or Steel-type Heavy Slam, so consider how you want to use it in battle when choosing the best TM! #PokemonGOtip #PokemonGO #Pokemon #Aggron
